♪ Well, I paid a visit ♪

00:09.926 --> 00:13.221
♪ While it's possible
I missed it ♪

00:13.304 --> 00:16.265
♪ It seemed different
yet exactly the same ♪

00:16.349 --> 00:18.268
♪ Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah ♪

00:18.351 --> 00:19.686
♪<i> Till further notice</i> ♪

00:19.769 --> 00:21.521
♪ Till further notice ♪

